  "text": "The classification of asymptotic bounds of forb(m, F ) with 4-rowed matrices F is due to [CITATION_1] . For this classification, we need the matrices defined in [CITATION_2] . Proof. We see that F satisfies the condition of the Corollary to Theorem 3.25 due to Theorem 6.5.",
